! Quasi-1D Superionic Carbon Hydride

A literature-indexed material anchor for thermally driven quasi-1D superionic
states in carbon hydride.

!! Why It Matters

This is not yet an integrated Research Stack mechanism, but it is a strong
external lead for 1D transport, channel, and phase-transition analogies.

